query:
SELECT
            ts.id as time_slot_id,
            NULL::INTEGER as session_id,
            r.id as room_id
        FROM time_slots ts
        CROSS JOIN rooms r
        WHERE NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1
            FROM timeslot_assignments ta
            WHERE ta.time_slot_id = ts.id
            AND ta.room_id = r.id
        )
        ORDER BY ts.start_time, r.id
